lead_paragraph: Jaye Marie Green won the LPGA Tour qualifying tournament Sunday to top the 20 card-earners, making a 20-foot birdie putt on the final hole for a one-stroke victory.

headline.print_headline: Jaye Marie Green Wins LPGA Tour Q-School
